---
// Collective-spend curve: an hourly line/area chart of how much the whole
// community spent through the day (UTC). The centerpiece of the reframed page —
// it shows WHEN the world is spending (working-hour peaks, overnight valleys),
// not who spent the most. Hidden until the client fetches GET /api/collective
// and injects an inline SVG into #graphBody (see lib/leaderboard.ts buildChart).
---

<section class="graph" id="graph" aria-label="Collective spend through the day" hidden>
  <div class="graph-head">
    <span class="graph-title">When we spend</span>
    <span class="graph-sub" id="graphSub"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="graph-body" id="graphBody"></div>
</section>
